comments: Quickley (NYK) grabs Butler's (MIA) right arm as he spins and the contact affects his SQBR.
Robinson (NYK) makes contact to Adebayo's (MIA) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bullock (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Adebayo (MIA) with his arms slightly extended, but the contact is marginal.
Burks (NYK) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Robinson (NYK) makes clean contact with the ball when he dislodges it from Adebayo (MIA).  The ensuing contact with Randle (NYK) is considered incidental.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Herro (MIA) and does not deliver contact.
Iguodala (MIA) makes marginal contact with his arm/shoulder to the front of Randle's (NYK) body as he begins his drive.
Burks (NYK) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Herro (MIA).
Butler (MIA) places his off-arm against Burks (NYK) but does not extend it into him or otherwise dislodge him from his defensive position as he brings the ball up the court.
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
